name: MSRI-DUO-GIFYGBV-R-01
description: v4w.enko - "MSRI-DUO-GIFYGBV-R-01" is a gif animation of  3d Object, generated with custom definition. 4 lofts are animated in 4 layers for each color: Yellow, Green, Blue, Violet. The cells of the Red  "3d voronoi" cube are linked to the attractor`s points of the lofts. The two parallel projections [Left and Front] are showing the different viewpoints of the same form. Total 128 frames, 512*1024px canvas.
